overview: BET's #1 rated show is about to get a whole lot hotter! Your horny hosts Porcha Carrera and King James get busy right off the top in this music-driven masterpiece, and from there it's a fantasy fuck fest that delivers scene after scene of booty-shakin' bumpin' and grindin'! Hilarious music video parodies from Kelly Divine as 'Lady Gag Gaga', Dawayne Dane as 'No Cents' and D Snoop as 'Dizzy Bone' getting swarmed by fans who want a whole lot more than just an autograph! Countdown to the 106 & Park clips that are way too hot for TV!
title: Official 106 & Park Parody
